      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though the suspension is beginning to feel its age and may need attention in the coming year. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable door dings, minor paint chips on the hood, and some fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear, particularly on the driver\u2019s seat, and the infotainment screen has a few dead pixels. It has been well-maintained mechanically with regular oil changes, but it is certainly not a show car.",
